query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'english',
'math',
'pt',
'salesforce')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('array',
'c++',
'conditional-probability',
'dynamical-systems',
'factorial',
'fourier-transform',
'homology-cohomology',
'html5',
'linear-programming',
'scripts',
'server',
'sobolev-spaces',
'substitution',
'supremum-and-infimum')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND a1.question_id = q1.id group by t1.name;
